                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Keira poses nude for art
                              Proud of figure                            
	London, Dec. 14 (PTI): Bend It Like Beckham star Keira Knightley visited the Halcyon Gallery here to pose nude for artist Mitch Griffiths.         
	Its considered a great honour to be painted by Mitch, a source told Daily Mail. He is a highly respected nude painter and is painting a number of subjects for an exhibition next year. He is delighted Keira agreed to take part, the source added.         
	Griffiths has been commissioned to paint a 12-feet-long canvas of 246 famous people, including Cindy Crawford, Claudia Schiffer, Will Smith and David Bowie, which will be auctioned.                                                                                                                                                          
